These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, dressmaker
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, july
1. the dressmaker is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Job           | dressmaker | designer |
| Birthday   | july     | june  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
2 different pets are kept: goat, lizard
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, satire
1. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Pet         | lizard   | goat      |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | satire |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, rock
There are 2 different nationalities: nigerian, dutch
1. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the right of the nigerian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Music-Genre   | rock | r&b    |
| Nationality     | nigerian | dutch |

 #################################

 
